---
import Button from "../shared/Button.astro";
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import ByNumber from "./ByNumber.astro";



---

<section class="relative pt-32 lg:pt-36" id="inicio">
    <Container className={"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12"}>
        <div class="absolute w-full lg:w-1/2 inset-y-0 lg:right-0 ">
            <span class="absolute -left-6 md:left-4 top-24 lg:top-28 w-24 h-24 rotate-90 skew-x-12 rounded-3xl bg-orange-700 blur-xl opacity-60 lg:opacity-95 lg:block hidden"></span>
            <span class="absolute right-4 bottom-12 w-24 h-24 rounded-3xl bg-primary blur-xl opacity-80"></span>
        </div>
        <span class="w-4/12 lg:w-2/12 aspect-square bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-yellow-300 absolute -top-5 lg:left-0 rounded-full skew-y-12 blur-2xl opacity-40 skew-x-12 rotate-90"></span>
        <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:text-left lg:py-7 xl:py-8 
        lg:items-start lg:max-w-none max-w-3xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:flex-1 lg:w-1/2">
            
            <h1 id="dynamic-text" class="text-5xl sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight xl:text-6xl/tight
             font-bold text-heading-1 lg:h-48">
             Desarrollo de <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 from-20%  to-red-600 transition-all">Software</span> hecho a la medida
            </h1>
            <script is:inline>
                const dynamicTextElement = document.getElementById('dynamic-text');
             

                const originalText = dynamicTextElement.innerText;

                let charIndex = 0;
                
                function typeText() {
                    if (charIndex < originalText.length) {
                    dynamicTextElement.innerText = originalText.slice(0, charIndex + 1);
                

                    charIndex++;
                    setTimeout(typeText, 25); 
                    }
                    if(charIndex == originalText.length){
                        dynamicTextElement.innerHTML = 'Desarrolo de <span id="final-text" class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 from-20% to-red-600 transition-all">Software</span> hecho a la medida';
                    }
                }
                typeText();
            </script>
            <Paragraph className="mt-8">
                Descubra cómo podemos ayudarle a alcanzar sus objetivos tecnológicos y superar sus desafíos. Desde la conceptualización y el diseño hasta el desarrollo, la implementación y el soporte continuo, estamos comprometidos a ser su socio tecnológico.
            </Paragraph>
